<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بَيَّض له ابن ابي حاتم.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وقال الدارقطني:</span> مجهول.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
